# ============================================================
#  nav-cam-detect — Environment Variables
#  Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the values.
# ============================================================

# ---- Google Cloud Vision API key (API KEY REQUIRED) --------
# OCR mode reads GPS coordinates + compass bearing directly off each
# frame's burned-in NavCam overlay. The pipeline will NOT function in
# OCR mode without a valid key.
#
# How to get one (free tier: 1000 image requests/month):
#   1. https://console.cloud.google.com  → create/select a project
#   2. Enable "Cloud Vision API"
#   3. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create API Key
#
# Paste the key below, save as `.env`, then:
#   docker compose down && docker compose up -d
#
GOOGLE_VISION_API_KEY=API_KEY_REQUIRED
